whats the best avg trolling speed for mahi mahi in mph aloha new boat owner thats yet to get a mahi ive been trolling about mph with skirts and a hard rapalla type lure called a marauder the marauder works i know from previous catches on the sail boat i used to work on but i never noticed the speed we were going any suggestions i live in hawaii btw the marauder is supposed to be trolled between and mph skirts a little faster than if you have both baits out i would try or also try alternating your speed once and a while another trick is to put the boat in neutral and let the baits sink i cant remember how many times i've hooked up while letting the baits rest for a minute or so also try fishing around floating debris i e weed lines floating drums large pieces of plywood etc anything that can provide cover for the mahi's prey hope this helps good luck Trolling for fish Fishing Angling Internet troll Striped bass Anchor Fishing rod Albatross Trapping Tlingit Seine (fishing) Yacht Fly fishing Second Battle of the Atlantic Speed limit Poker jargon USS Tunny (SS-282) First Battle of the Atlantic Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Battle of Jutland Glossary of nautical terms Skateboarding trick Teen Girl Squad Big-game fishing USS Thresher (SS-200) USS Yorktown (CV-5) Sailing Multihull USS Whale (SS-239) Kitesurfing Advance fee fraud Age of Mythology Giant squid Animal Crossing Fast bowling Trawling Naval mine USS Trathen (DD-530) USS Tang (SS-306) Kayak Computer virus Rail tracks USS Harder (SS-257) USS Sea Devil (SS-400) The Hobbit USS Wasp (CV-7) USS Atule (SS-403) Perch One Piece minor characters Windsurfing 24 Hours of Le Mans USS Wichita (CA-45) USS Wahoo (SS-238) Interstate Highway High-speed rail Sea-Monkey RuneScape skills Kalimdor Glenn Curtiss The Inside Episodes of Lost (Season 1) USS Trepang (SS-412) Cruising (maritime) 1980 eruption of Mount St. Helens Eastern Kingdoms Boat Submarine Speed of light Piccolo Junior Saga Motorway USS Zane (DD-337) Battle o